text: Moses, therefore, gave to the children of Gad and of Reuben, and to the half-tribe of Manasseh, the son of Joseph, the kingdom of Sihon, king of the Amorites, and the kingdom of Agh-king of Bassan, and their land and the cities thereof roundabout.
